h1 Login, good sir.
- if ('undefined' !== typeof errors && errors.length)
  ul#errors
    - each error in errors
      li.error= error
p Or 
  a(href="/register") register
  | ?
form(action="/login", method="POST")
  label email:
    br
    input(name="email")
  br
  label password:
    br
    input(type="password", name="password")
  br
  input(type="submit", value="Login")
